‚ùå **Code and Technical Content**
- Source code (Python, JavaScript, etc.)
- Code comments and docstrings
- Variable names and function names
- SQL queries and database schemas
- Configuration files (YAML, JSON, ENV)
- Git commit messages
- API endpoint names
- Error messages and log statements

‚ùå **Documentation Files**
- README.md files
- Technical documentation (.md files in docs/)
- Implementation guides
- Architecture documents
- API documentation
- User guides and tutorials
- Changelog entries
- Migration guides

‚ùå **User-Facing Content**
- UI text and labels
